name: WestJet 767-338ER(WL) [C-FWAD] Smoky Landing and Taxi at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
A quick clip from 2016! Here we have C-FWAD, WestJet's 3rd 767 making a smokey touchdown on 17L, from London-Gatwick. WestJet currently operates 3 times a week from Calgary to London for the winter, increasing back to 5 times a week starting in the summer. ATC is included, enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
